Resource Profile: VAERS Patient

Official URL: http://va.gov/fhir/StructureDefinition/VAERSPatient Version: 1.5.30
Draft as of 2025-05-25 Computable Name: VAERSPatient

This StructureDefinition contains the maps for ADERS to us-core-patient.

​See also the FHIR Shorthand.
